categorize the vulnerabilities of core components according to\npotential threats for the locking key in logic locking schemes. Furthermore, we\npropose several defense layers and countermeasures to protect the device from\nthose vulnerabilities. Finally, we turn our focus to open research questions\nand conclude with suggestions for future research directions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 20 Jul 2019 20:03:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-23"}
