h very high precision, of the order\nof $(2$-$6)\\times10^{-6}$ $\\rm pc\\,cm^{-3}$, owing to the microsecond level\ntiming achievable for this pulsar at the MWA's low frequencies. This\nunderscores the usefulness of low-frequency observations for probing the ISM\ntoward PTA pulsars and informing optimal observing strategies for PTA\nexperiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 21 Jul 2019 05:28:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-25"}
